headline: Zevia and Lamb Weston Shares Are Soaring, What You Need To Know

headline: How To Earn $500 A Month From Lamb Weston Stock Ahead Of Q1 Earnings
summary: Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) will release earnings results for the first quarter, before the opening bell on Tuesday, Sept. 30. Analysts expect the company to report quarterly earnings at 53 cents per share. That’s down from 73 cents per share in the year-ago period. Lamb Weston projects to report quarterly revenue at $1.62 billion. It generated $1.65 billion the previous year, according to data from Benzinga Pro.
